emotes.msg: Very good, you may keep your cestus. A lady near Zaikhal named Devana bint Hamudi is looking for skilled hunters.
Give this to her.
HamudsDemiseStarted_0511
I seek the teeth of certain creatures, the gromnies.  But I won't take just anything, I want only the most well preserved gromnie teeth!
Give me the rare tooth of the fierce gromnies, and I will craft it into something useful.  I will also take auroch horns.
I require stout gromnie teeth for my craft!
I am still experimenting with the skulls of certain skeletons.  They don't seem to be good for weapons, but I'll give you a health potion for them.
AcidAxeTurnedIn

Nasty for you, if they catch you on one of these, eh?
There you are, a bit of a reward and I've made a nice spear from the horn.
Fire Auroch horns are beyond my skill, but I can trade for them. Here, take this reward.
I've heard about some master bowyer named Yuan Hanzu who makes these into bows.
Hmmm, yes, I'll take this horn. I may just trade this for something I can use. Here's your reward.
I think Yuan Hanzu, the Sho master bowyer, makes great bows from these horns.
Well, this tooth is neither that of a gromnie, nor an auroch. I used to avoid trading for these, but I've learned they have offensive properties.
As you can see, this mace will now do some nasty piercing damage.
Ah, one of the smaller Niffis shells. With a special technique I have devised I can flatten and reform these.
Here, I made this shield yesterday. That's sure to make quite a statement on the battlefield.
Hehe, the shell almost looks like a helmet now. With just a little work...
There you are! A beautiful Niffis Shell Helm.
Oh, what a beautiful niffis orb! You deserve a reward worthy of this find.
Don't hesitate to bring me more of these opalescent marvels.
These teeth are light and will fly well. They just won't do as much damage as some of your higher end spiketails.
These teeth are light and will fly well. They just won't do as much damage as some of your higher end atlatl darts.
You might get more if you put this under your pillow, haha!
Jade tooth eh? These are just the right weight for bolt heads.
Enjoy!
Swamp Gromnie teeth are exceptionally sharp. Ow! See what I mean?
Be careful with those.
This reminds me, A lady near Zaikhal is looking for hunters.
Here is your reward. If you wish to know more, hand the dagger back to me as a sign of trust.
It has taken me a few years, but I have finally figured out a use for Sable Gromnie teeth.
It has taken me a few years, but I have finally figured out a use for Ebon Gromnie teeth.
The Brass Gromnie only recently appeared on Marae Lassel. Had I not been inspired to craft, I wouldn't have even thought of making this out of Brass Gromnie teeth!
The Copper Gromnie only recently appear on Marae Lassel. Had I not been inspired to craft, I wouldn't have even thought of making this out of Copper Gromnie teeth!
I hope you don't think me macabre for collecting these.
I will give a greater reward for more unique skeleton skulls.
This skull is very unique, it will be extremely useful to me.
Thank you for bringing me this treasure.
Yes, I have found a use for these. I'll have to cleanse the skull first of course. Yech!!
I know of a sage somewhere in the southern mountain range that also collects these.
Tibia from a grievver if I am not mistaken. Interesting bone structure.
Thank you, bring me more of these and you will receive the same reward.
A Tusker Slave tusk. You can't use these on the Island of the Tuskers. It's a good thing you came to me.
These tusks are exceptionally useful since they are hollow.
Well Done! I expect the Lich didn't give this willingly.
Please convince more Liches to part with their bones.
A thighbone... hmmm, not a Dark Revenant, but I can still use it.
Bring me a Dark Revenant thighbone I will reward you fivefold.
Aha! A Dark Revenant thighbone, quite exceptional!
A fine reward for your formidable deed.
Hard to imagine that they used this as body ornamentation. Thankfully, we can use these as an augmentation of sorts.
This is a nice find. I have a friend that would like this. Thank you, and here is your reward.

Oh I agree... It isn't really enough, so take this too.
Hmm, if we stretch this a little here and disjoint the jaw. We can twist this little bit and then, excellent! Wear this with pride.
Since the helmet doesn't really offer much protection, I think a little monetary reward is in order as well.

Well. This is a little fleshy. Of course we can pull this, oh blech, what was that? Well whatever it was, this poor sod won't need it. Oh and the smell, well, let's just add a little touch of sunflower oil. Much better.
Here you go.
A grim looking shell. The Niffis are never this dark. Well I'll see what I can craft from it.
Odd, there seems to be magic within the shell that was left within when I finished the shield. You might be able to affix a symbol if you center on this shield.
A mite! This large? You're pulling my leg...
Let's see what I can do with this. Shave a little off here and here and...Well that is odd. I seem to have loosed some hidden qualities within the bones.
Good luck with this.
These fangs are very sharp. Pried them from a carenzi you say. Well, I think that I can get them into some useful form.
A wrap here...done.
They seem to have been magically enchanted while within the beast. I find this strange and somewhat frightening.
